movie_name: Sayonara subete no Evangerion: Anno Hideaki no 1214-nichi
short_description: EVANGELION is coming to an end. NHK spent 4 years with exclusive access to director Hideaki Anno, documenting the creative process behind the final EVANGELION film. For the first time, the camera is allowed inside Anno's studio.
